[normal]nce, particularly b
[normal]ecause all of the other authorities are urban.  After all, 50% of the population of Northumberland is rural, and they have as much call to have their particular needs provided for as th
[normal]ose of the urban population are, but if representation is constituted a
[normal]s it is proposed at present, the likelihood is that they would have no true and accurate representation at all.
